title: Amy Has To Cancel Her Trip to Haiti + Vince Gill Plays “Did Vince Gill Say It’ Game + Bobby Gets Response From Text He Sent to New Girl

description:
Amy reveals that she will no longer be going on her trip to Haiti because it’s too dangerous. Vince Gill stops by and Bobby Gets an update on the girl he DM’d yesterday trying to go out with.
